    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/cfc3e308c5fe9060bbaeea31a1503f33.avif?t=1772386407\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras_big/cfc3e308c5fe9060bbaeea31a1503f33.avif?t=1772386407 width=800 height=621 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《预言之牌》结合了塔防、卡组构建和Roguelike元素，并深受集换式卡牌游戏（TCG）的启发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构建一个不断进化的法术和怪物卡组。融合、防御、打开卡包，创造新的策略。重复。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用你的卡牌召唤强大的怪物并施放强力法术！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/d76d8b049c285a8ee6e5084af7a9137d.poster.avif?t=1772386407\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/d76d8b049c285a8ee6e5084af7a9137d.webm?t=1772386407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/d76d8b049c285a8ee6e5084af7a9137d.mp4?t=1772386407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着游戏的进行，逐步构建你的卡组，并在途中发现新的策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个怪物都有其独特的效果，所以一定要明智地使用它们！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细考虑你将使用的法术！它们不是怪物，但这并不意味着法术不强大！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张卡牌都会与随机生成的地图互动，因此战略位置至关重要！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>融合你的卡牌，创造全新的怪物！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/5c39599009f1f124f176c4f0229e34da.poster.avif?t=1772386407\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/5c39599009f1f124f176c4f0229e34da.webm?t=1772386407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/5c39599009f1f124f176c4f0229e34da.mp4?t=1772386407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用融合法术卡，你可以将两只怪物融合成一个拥有极强效果的新怪物！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每次游戏结束后，打开一个全新的卡包！整个卡牌收藏等着你去发现！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/1ec4a3fd6a87048ac96ec86bab774a46.poster.avif?t=1772386407\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/1ec4a3fd6a87048ac96ec86bab774a46.webm?t=1772386407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/1ec4a3fd6a87048ac96ec86bab774a46.mp4?t=1772386407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏结束后，你会获得金币，用来购买新的卡包。谁知道里面有什么？也许会有惊喜……</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有超过100张卡牌等待你去发掘，每一张都能以不同的方式帮助你获得胜利！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>途中结识一位小伙伴</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/deffd9ef52e5a9f66b99b132a68f7e86.poster.avif?t=1772386407\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/deffd9ef52e5a9f66b99b132a68f7e86.webm?t=1772386407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/deffd9ef52e5a9f66b99b132a68f7e86.mp4?t=1772386407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的可爱小狗会陪伴你一路前行，它是不是超可爱？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个游戏模式都有你的小伙伴不同的皮肤！</p></li></ul>",
